{"tid":1611742,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[放負] 其實點樣先算贏？","createTime":"2019-10-02T04:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T04:54:56.000Z","uid":302578,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c2dbaa581adccecb9af7f8165a48740d0df8d088","tid":1611742,"uid":302578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:45:52.000Z","msg":"一百幾日喇<br />\n老實講勇武打贏狗就冇可能 話曬人地有無限裝備<br />\n正苦又表明唔撚會理我地任何訴求<br />\n我地成日話贏左就煲底見<br />\n但係點樣先係「贏」？<br />\n見唔到曙光呀屌...<br />\n雖然話和勇不分<br />\n但係如果繼續呢個pattern<br />\n勇武的確會用盡<br />\n我自己每次越行越前<br />\n和理非 物資鏈 搬鐵馬 擋子彈<br />\n俾人拉真係時間問題<br />\n<br />\n點先叫贏呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎屌我失敗主義<br />\n但係真係想知大家覺得贏嘅scenerio係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">好撚攰呀屌</span></span>"},{"pid":"1d0c64094e1e03c4a8744a654f159625e0b1eaf0","tid":1611742,"uid":268548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:47:09.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"0f74bce7798bc3e5292982dd5f40cd5b213bb4c3","tid":1611742,"uid":53000,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:51:07.000Z","msg":"唔好氣餒<br />\n攰就放空下<br />\n去個旅行，唔好留意新聞<br />\n調整下個心情<br />\n<br />\n呢幾個月好多人心情同你一樣<br />\n真係要抖一抖再出發<br />\n唔駛驚冇左你唔得<br />\n仲有其他手足頂住<br />\n<br />\n宣佈有 真普選，撤銷所有控罪 同 清算警隊<br />\n就係贏嗰一日"},{"pid":"3ba0b63f3f67b129bdbafccf0989c1bc66f2bbb1","tid":1611742,"uid":93277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:54:56.000Z","msg":"耐力賽，一路影響經濟等班商家有錢佬出手，睇13:30，有錢佬遲早搞鳩林鄭<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DUgpanK7EjQ&amp;t=869s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDUgpanK7EjQ%26t%3D869s&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdLnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=c8afa7bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DUgpanK7EjQ&amp;t=869s</a>"}]}